<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_524" id="261r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_524_r1l2">Der Stat cʒu krewſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_524_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . vvie daʒ <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒwiſchen Beÿrewt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r1l4">krewſen ermort ſeÿ den Jr gen krewſen in daʒ gericht gefürt . vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r1l6">auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtanden</expan> habt er ſulle <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener geweſen ſein 
<add><ab facs="#facs_524_r1l5"><expan>gen<ex>an</ex>t</expan> der ſwab </ab></add> etc ~ daʒ <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r1l7">wir vvol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd danken deʒ eẅr <expan>frewndſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> fleiſʒıklıchen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r1l8"><expan>Bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> euch mit ernſt daʒ Jr fürbaʒ eẅr vorſch darnach habt von wem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r1l9"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> in welche vveiʒ der mort geſchehen ſeÿ / vnd was Jr dauon alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r1l10">erfürt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> erfaren het / daʒ lieſʒt vns beÿ diſem <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex>ſelbs</expan> botten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r1l12"> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> wiſſen / daʒ bottenlon wir 
<del rend="strikethrough">gern </del> becʒalen . vnd daʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_524_r1l11">vmb </ab></add> eẅr <expan>Erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r1l13">gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> wellen ~ <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ıj̃ / <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> dÿoniſij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_524" id="261r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Krewsen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie daz
                                <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> czwischen Beyrewt und Krewsen ermort
                        sey, den ir gen Krewsen in daz gericht gefürt, und auch
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>standen</expan> habt, er sulle
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener gewesen sein,
                                    <add><expan>gen<ex>an</ex>t</expan> der Swab</add>, etc., daz
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und danken dez ewr
                                <expan>frewndsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> fleisziklichen, und
                                <expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> euch mit ernst, daz ir fürbaz ewr
                        vorsch darnach habt, von wem <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> in welche weiz der
                        mort geschehen sey; und was ir davon also erfürt
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> erfaren het, daz lieszt uns bey disem
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex>selbs</expan> botten
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> wissen, daz bottenlon
                        wir beczalen und daz <add>umb</add> ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> wellen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Dyonisii.
                    </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
